Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:56.07,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(434,472)}38（t）坦克等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:56.07,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,540)}活用速度快的特點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:56.07,Zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)}{\an7}{\pos(132,590)}以偵查為主要任務
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走攻守相當全面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為所有戰車主力的中型坦克
